name: Kindan no Pet - Seaman - Gaze Hakase no Jikken-tou 2001-nen Taiouban Rev A [SDC]
description:
Created for the GMTK Game Jam, with the theme: 'Out of Control'.

This is just a small touhou-like bullet hell where you dodge a crap ton of projectiles coming for you, but something is wrong...

Might cause mild to severe frustration or annoyance.
